&lt;h2

&lt;h4&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About commercetools&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Real innovation starts with a strong foundation, and at commercetools, that comes from the perfect balance of our product and our people.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Behind every leap forward is a collective of builders, explorers, doers, makers, and problem-solvers. The kind of people who not only created composable commerce but also shaped the culture of experimentation that idea unlocked. Together they are the engine of commerce innovation today.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;At commercetools, we power the next era of commerce for our customers. Whether it’s AI-driven solutions that help enterprises make smarter business decisions, bridging digital and physical shopping experiences, or enabling entirely new ways for industries to connect with their customers, we help the world’s most ambitious companies experiment, scale, and grow without limits.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note: This role is located &lt;strong&gt;in London&lt;/strong&gt; and we are offering a &lt;strong&gt;hybrid working model with a minimum of 4 days per week&lt;/strong&gt; in our Holborn office.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why This Role?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you ready to kickstart your career in tech sales? We’re looking for an ambitious, curious Business Development Representative (BDR) to join our team in London.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Here, the best idea wins, not the loudest voice. You will have the tools, trust, and space to not only build the future of commerce, but to build your own.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This isn’t just a stepping stone—it’s a launchpad.&lt;/strong&gt; In this role, you will work hand-in-hand with our Account Executives (AEs) &lt;strong&gt;to conquer the French and Benelux markets&lt;/strong&gt;. We are deeply invested in your growth, offering a clear, structured career development path designed to fast-track you into an AE or specialized sales role as you master the craft.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Your Impact (What you’ll be doing)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll be the first point of contact for future customers:&lt;/strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;helping us spark new relationships and drive long-term growth.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Partner with AEs: &lt;/strong&gt;Team up with Account Executives to strategize and open doors in the thriving French and Benelux regions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Spark Conversations: &lt;/strong&gt;Connect with potential clients through creative outreach (phone, email, and social media) and qualify leads from our marketing campaigns.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Consult &amp;amp; Connect:&lt;/strong&gt; Chat with prospective clients, understand their unique business challenges, and introduce them to our game-changing products.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Set the Stage: &lt;/strong&gt;Book high-quality meetings and discovery calls for our AE team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Be the Face of the Brand:&lt;/strong&gt; Represent us at our industry-leading events and give engaging presentations to potential clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Never Stop Learning:&lt;/strong&gt; Stay sharp by keeping up-to-date with our latest product features, pricing models, and commerce trends.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What Will Set You Apart&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Great ideas come from many paths, and your unique perspective matters more than checking every box. We value mindset, drive, and curiosity over years of experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’ll be a great fit if:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You speak the language: &lt;/strong&gt;You are business-fluent in French (or German) and English (written and spoken).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;You’re a

