&lt;li&gt;Oversee intricate domestic and international travel logistics, ensuring seamless itineraries from start to finish.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Join key leadership meetings to capture action items, organize all-hands and onsite events, and help facilitate quarterly business cadences.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Engage with relevant Slack channels to help maintain team organization, share reminders, and keep regional teams connected.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with our Europe-based Workplace Experience team to keep the Boston office welcoming and functional, while organizing engaging local events that bring our Boston team together.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
